[normal]There is lots of evidence to substantiate this, but most recently in May 2013, an 
[normal]Ofsted
[normal] report found that 
[normal]schools are failing children and young people by not meeting the set 
[normal]statutory guidance on SRE, but equally there is a lack of accountability surrounding SRE and PSHE generally, highlighted by there being no set curriculum to deliver, and poor assessment (
[normal]Not yet good enough: personal, social, health and economic education in schools, 
[normal]Ofsted
[normal], May 2013
